{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "圣树 第20章 4-4 祈祷的条件",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "强力结界封锁住了通往上层的道路。\\n奈迪犹请求塞西娅帮忙解除结界，\\n但塞西娅因不知道他的真实身份\\n无法进行判断而拒绝了他。为了说服\\n塞西娅，奈迪犹开始讲述自己的身世。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "圣树·下层\\n登云巨枝",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "总算到了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "格外粗壮的树枝向上延伸……\\n仿佛能直达云端……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "只要顺着那个树枝前进，\\n就能到达圣树的上层。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "塞西娅，你怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这里流动着一股\\n未知的沉重魔力。\\n究竟是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "呵呵，不愧是伊莉雅的巫女大人，\\n已经发现了吗。请看吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "这股力量是……结界吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "正是。不幸的是，\\n这个结界导致精灵\\n也无法继续前进。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "什么意思？\\n不是你们布下的结界吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这个结界并非是通过\\n精灵族秘术之力布下的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "这个结界是谁布下的，\\n结界的力量之源又是什么——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "长久以来被谜团\\n所笼罩的真相\\n终于被我们找到了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "而答案就在被你们\\n称为炼狱文书的书里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "在炼狱文书里！？\\n难道伊莉雅教和这个结界\\n有什么关联吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "我倒想对你解释这其中的缘由，\\n可惜我们没那么多时间。\\n我就直接告诉你结论吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "能够解除这个结界的人，\\n就是塞西娅你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我……能解除结界？\\n为什么是我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "只要你让意念与结界同步，\\n应该就能知道答案。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "原来你们是为了\\n让我解除这个结界\\n才把我带到这里来的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "那么也就是说……\\n只要我妹妹拒绝祈祷，\\n你们将无法继续前进。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "是的，你说对了。\\n如果是那样，就有点难办了呢。\\n奈迪犹，到时我们该怎么办呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "祈祷需要用强大的意念\\n传送魔力，所以不能\\n强人所难。不过……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "塞西娅，你应该清楚，\\n这个世界充满了虚伪。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "伊莉雅教诞生的原委、\\n魔神的真相，还有你哥哥\\n第七王子与我掉过包这些事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你新了解到的事，\\n和你之前一直坚信的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你内心已经逐渐意识到了\\n哪个才是真的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你一直坚信的世界\\n不过是他人营造的虚假世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你就不想知道为什么\\n会发生这种事吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你不想粉碎虚伪，\\n为世界带来名为真相的光吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "若你有一丝这样的想法，\\n就解除这个结界吧。\\n答案就在这棵树的顶端。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "不得不承认……\\n我所知道的历史是\\n经他人有意篡改的产物。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "要说我不想知道历史\\n为什么会被篡改成现在这样，\\n那肯定是假的……不过——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我想知道真相是一回事，\\n而你是否值得信赖\\n是另一回事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你和哥哥有着\\n一目了然的相似之处，\\n让我无法把你当作陌生人……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我也不认为你所说的\\n都是凭空捏造出来的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "但不可忽视的是，\\n你的话里还有很多疑点，\\n比如，关于你自己的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "按照你的说法，\\n你被龙鳞病所侵蚀，\\n应该早已不在人世。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "那你究竟是什么人？\\n与龙缔结新的契约\\n又有什么目的？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "不知道这些答案的话，\\n我无法决定\\n是否要献上祈祷。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "原来如此，你是想用\\n奈迪犹的情报做交换啊。\\n真是个难对付的巫女大人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "接下来要怎么办呢？\\n奈迪犹，就看你的了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "……\\n好吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "你要答应我，\\n如果你对我的回答感到满意，\\n就要献上祈祷。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我作为亚罗拉斯的子嗣\\n出生在阿尔贝里亚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "身体遭到龙鳞病的侵蚀，\\n出生后不久便丧了命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "迄今为止我所说的\\n没有半句是谎言。\\n这就告诉你故事的后续吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_07_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}